OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1781287881
OL,3,CSara Sharif siblings remain in
OL,4,CPakistan as council has no choice but
OL,5,Cto withdraw
OL,7,FThe siblings of 10-year-old Sara
OL,8,FSharif who was murdered by her father
OL,9,Fand stepmother in Surrey will stay in
OL,10,FPakistan after the local council had
OL,11,Fto withdraw from a legal case to
OL,12,Freturn them to Britain.
OL,14,FThe five children were made wards of
OL,15,Fcourt and Surrey Council Council tried
OL,16,Fto bring them back through courts in
OL,17,FPakistan.
OL,19,FBut their grandfather wanted the
OL,20,Fsiblings to stay with him in Jhelum,
OL,21,Fnorth-eastern Pakistan.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/10
