FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1781287881
OL,3,CSara Sharif siblings remain in
OL,4,CPakistan as council has no choice but
OL,5,Cto withdraw
OL,7,FSurrey Council Council said it had no
OL,8,Fway of pursuing the application in
OL,9,FPakistan with English proceedings
OL,10,Fcoming to an end and therefore had no
OL,11,Fchoice but to withdraw.
OL,13,FTerence Herbert, Chief Executive of
OL,14,FSurrey County Council, said: "Surrey
OL,15,FCounty Council has done everything
OL,16,Fwithin our power to support the
OL,17,Fsiblings and half siblings of Sara
OL,18,FSharif in Pakistan.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1781287881
OL,3,CSara Sharif siblings remain in
OL,4,CPakistan as council has no choice but
OL,5,Cto withdraw
OL,7,F"The children were made Wards of the
OL,8,FHigh Court and an Order was sought to
OL,9,Freturn the children to England.
OL,11,F"The High Court gave permission for
OL,12,Fthe council to make an application to
OL,13,Fthe High Court in Lahore to seek to
OL,14,Fsecure the return of the children and
OL,15,Fthat application was made.
OL,17,F"The English court proceedings are
OL,18,Fabout to come to an end, which means
OL,19,Fthe Pakistan Proceedings in Lahore
OL,20,Fhave concluded."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
