CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1781287881
OL,3,CSara Sharif siblings remain in
OL,4,CPakistan as council has no choice but
OL,5,Cto withdraw
OL,7,FSara, 10, was "failed by the
OL,8,Fsafeguarding system" before she was
OL,9,Fmurdered by her father Urfan Sharif
OL,10,Fand stepmother Beinash Batool in 2023,
OL,11,Faccording to a review into her death.
OL,13,FShe was taken out of school, a move
OL,14,Fwhich the review found was made "to
OL,15,Fkeep Sara hidden from view in the last
OL,16,Fweeks of her life".
OL,18,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1781287881
OL,3,CSara Sharif siblings remain in
OL,4,CPakistan as council has no choice but
OL,5,Cto withdraw
OL,7,FSara was found dead at the family home
OL,8,Fin Woking, Surrey, in August 2023.
OL,10,FSharif and Batool were jailed for life
OL,11,Fwith minimum terms of 40 years and 33
OL,12,Fyears respectively in 2024, after
OL,13,Fbeing found guilty of her murder.
OL,15,FSara's uncle, Faisal Malik, was found
OL,16,Fguilty of causing or allowing her
OL,17,Fdeath and jailed for 16 years.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
