FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1781287881
OL,3,CSara Sharif siblings remain in
OL,4,CPakistan as council has no choice but
OL,5,Cto withdraw
OL,7,FA lengthy review concluded there had
OL,8,Fbeen multiple missed opportunities to
OL,9,Fsave Sara from harm and that she was
OL,10,F"failed by the safeguarding system".
OL,12,FTheir trial heard how Sharif had
OL,13,Frepeated contact with Surrey social
OL,14,Fservices before he was charged with
OL,15,Fmurdering his daughter.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
