OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1781287881
OL,3,CSara Sharif siblings remain in
OL,4,CPakistan as council has no choice but
OL,5,Cto withdraw
OL,7,FA review into the handling of Sara's
OL,8,Fcare by various different services
OL,9,Fincluding police, health, social care
OL,10,Fand education, said she had been "a
OL,11,Fvictim of domestic abuse from birth
OL,12,Fonwards".
OL,14,FWhile she was described as a
OL,15,F"beautiful little girl, full of
OL,16,Fpersonality with a lovely smile", her
OL,17,F"reality was day-to-day abuse which
OL,18,Fbecame normalised", persuaded by her
OL,19,Ffather and stepmother "that she
OL,20,Fdeserved the treatment being meted out
OL,21,Fto her", the report said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1781287881
OL,3,CSara Sharif siblings remain in
OL,4,CPakistan as council has no choice but
OL,5,Cto withdraw
OL,7,FKnown as a local child safeguarding
OL,8,Fpractice review, the report described
OL,9,Fthe little girl's family life as
OL,10,F"complicated" and stated that those
OL,11,Fconvicted over her death were
OL,12,F"ultimately responsible".
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1781287881
OL,3,CSara Sharif siblings remain in
OL,4,CPakistan as council has no choice but
OL,5,Cto withdraw
OL,7,FBut the 62-page review, published on
OL,8,FThursday, said there were "many points
OL,9,Fat which different action could, and
OL,10,Fwe suggest, should, have been taken",
OL,11,Fthat there had been a "great deal of
OL,12,Finformation" available to various
OL,13,Fauthorities during her lifetime, and
OL,14,Fthat Sara "was not protected from
OL,15,Fabuse and torture".
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
